screen.COLOR_SCREEN=颜色
screen.COLOR_SCREEN.comment=包含色彩增强和交叉处理(色彩过滤器).

screen.DOF_SCREEN=景深
screen.DOF_SCREEN.comment=调整景深相关的设置.

screen.NORMALMAP_SCREEN=凹凸映射
screen.NORMALMAP_SCREEN.comment=启用凹凸和视差效果,如果资源包支持的话.

screen.MOTION_SCREEN=动态模糊
screen.MOTION_SCREEN.comment=调整动态模糊相关的设置.

screen.REFLECTIONS_SCREEN=反射
screen.REFLECTIONS_SCREEN.comment=调整反射相关的设置.

screen.SHADOWS_SCREEN=阴影
screen.SHADOWS_SCREEN.comment=包含阴影相关的设置,比如阴影距离.

screen.SKY_SCREEN=天空
screen.SKY_SCREEN.comment=包含天空相关的设置,比如体积光.

screen.WAVING_SCREEN=摇晃
screen.WAVING_SCREEN.comment=包含草、小麦、树叶等.

screen.MISC_SCREEN=杂项
